question: [["text","Urete povrch tlesa na obrzku:"],["img",11210],["input",{"answer":["132"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["textlatex","Urete povrch tlesa sloenho z krychl, kter maj dlku hrany $a=2$:"],["img",11208],["input",{"answer":["88"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["text","Urete povrch tlesa na obrzku:"],["img",11212],["input",{"answer":["120"],"style":"separate"}]]
explanation: [["textlatex","Povrch tlesa = 6 tverc + 8 obdlnk: $S=6\\cdot(\\frac{a}{2})^2+8\\cdot\\frac{a}{2}\\cdot b=6\\cdot2^2+8\\cdot2\\cdot6=24+96=120$"]]

question: [["text","Urete povrch tlesa na obrzku:"],["img",11215],["input",{"answer":["96"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["text","Urete povrch tlesa na obrzku:"],["img",11209],["input",{"answer":["48"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["textlatex","Pravideln tybok jehlan m povrch $S=28$ a obsah plt $S_{pl}=12$. Jak je dlka podstavn hrany $a$?"],["input",{"answer":["4"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["textlatex","Urete povrch koule, kter m objem $V=36 \\pi$."],["instructions","#exercise_vpisovacka-template_zaokrouhlete_cele#"],["input",{"answer":["113"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["text","Urete povrch tlesa na obrzku:"],["img",11227],["instructions","#exercise_vpisovacka-template_zaokrouhlete_cele#"],["input",{"answer":["69"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["textlatex","Jak je polomr koule, kter m objem $V= \\frac{32}{3}\\pi$?"],["instructions","#exercise_vpisovacka-template_zaokrouhlete_cele#"],["input",{"answer":["2"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["textlatex","Kuel m objem $V=22$ a vku $v=6$. Jak je obsah podstavy $S_p$?"],["instructions","#exercise_vpisovacka-template_zaokrouhlete_cele#"],["input",{"answer":["11"],"style":"separate"}]]
explanation: [["textlatex","Dosadme do vzorce pro objem kuele: $V=\\frac{1}{3}S_p\\cdot v \\Rightarrow  22=\\frac{1}{3}\\cdot S_p \\cdot 6 \\Rightarrow 22=2S_p \\Rightarrow S_p=11$"]]

question: [["textlatex","Urete objem kuele, kter m prmr podstavy $d=4$ a vku $v=12$."],["instructions","#exercise_vpisovacka-template_zaokrouhlete_cele#"],["input",{"answer":["50"],"style":"separate"}]]
explanation: [["textlatex","Objem kuele je $V=\\frac{1}{3}\\pi r^2 v=\\frac{1}{3}\\pi(\\frac{d}{2})^2 v=\\frac{1}{3}\\cdot \\pi\\cdot(\\frac{4}{2}) ^2\\cdot12=\\frac{1}{3}\\cdot \\pi\\cdot4\\cdot12=16\\pi\\approx50$"]]

question: [["textlatex","Kuel m objem $V=75\\pi$ a vku $v=9$. Jak je polomr podstavy kuele?"],["instructions","#exercise_vpisovacka-template_zaokrouhlete_cele#"],["input",{"answer":["5"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["textlatex","Vlec m objem $V=8\\pi$ a vku stejnou jako polomr podstavy. Jak je polomr podstavy vlce?"],["instructions","#exercise_vpisovacka-template_zaokrouhlete_cele#"],["input",{"answer":["2"],"style":"separate"}]]
explanation: [["textlatex","Dosadme $v=r$ do vzorce pro objem vlce: $V=\\pi r^2 v=\\pi r^3\\Rightarrow 8\\pi=\\pi r^3 \\Rightarrow 8=r^3\\Rightarrow r=2$"]]

question: [["text","Urete objem tlesa na obrzku:"],["img",11681],["instructions","#exercise_vpisovacka-template_zaokrouhlete_cele#"],["input",{"answer":["113"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["text","Urete objem tlesa na obrzku:"],["img",11685],["instructions","#exercise_vpisovacka-template_zaokrouhlete_cele#"],["input",{"answer":["172"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["textlatex","Kuel m obsah podstavy $S_p=10$ a obsah plt $S_{pl}=14$. Jak je povrch kuele?"],["instructions","#exercise_vpisovacka-template_zaokrouhlete_cele#"],["input",{"answer":["24"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["textlatex","Vlec m obsah plt $S_{pl}=24\\pi$ a vku $v=4$. Jak je polomr podstavy vlce?"],["instructions","#exercise_vpisovacka-template_zaokrouhlete_cele#"],["input",{"answer":["3"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["textlatex","Vlec m povrch $S=90\\pi$ a obsah plt $S_{pl}=40\\pi$. Jak je polomr podstavy vlce?"],["instructions","#exercise_vpisovacka-template_zaokrouhlete_cele#"],["input",{"answer":["5"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["text","Urete povrch tlesa na obrzku:"],["img",11681],["instructions","#exercise_vpisovacka-template_zaokrouhlete_cele#"],["input",{"answer":["170"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["text","Urete povrch tlesa na obrzku:"],["img",11685],["instructions","#exercise_vpisovacka-template_zaokrouhlete_cele#"],["input",{"answer":["188"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["text","Urete povrch tlesa na obrzku:"],["img",11682],["instructions","#exercise_vpisovacka-template_zaokrouhlete_cele#"],["input",{"answer":["50"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["text","Urete povrch tlesa na obrzku:"],["img",11684],["instructions","#exercise_vpisovacka-template_zaokrouhlete_cele#"],["input",{"answer":["151"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["textlatex","Kruh m obvod $o=8 \\pi$. Jak m obsah?"],["instructions","Odpov zaokrouhlete na cel slo."],["input",{"answer":["50"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["textlatex","tverec $ABCD$ m obvod $o=24$. Jak je obsah kruhu $k$?"],["img",13776],["instructions","Odpov zaokrouhlete na cel slo."],["input",{"answer":["28"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["textlatex","Obdlnk na obrzku m obsah $S=6$. Jak m obvod?"],["img",13786],["input",{"answer":["10"],"style":"separate"}]]

question: [["textlatex","Obdlnk na obrzku m obsah $S=8$. Del strana je dvojnsobek krat strany. Jak m obdlnk obvod?"],["img",13774],["input",{"answer":["12"],"style":"separate"}]]
